{"tid":2128600,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解返工食飯嗰一粒鐘過得寧舍快？","createTime":"2020-07-28T05:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T10:37:24.000Z","uid":87337,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"352a88f958b3ab5016dabbb78af1058cbd967004","tid":2128600,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"12點半放飯<br />\n宜家武肺就算未禁堂食我都係買返黎食<br />\n去完洗手間等𨋢落去<br />\n已經12點8<br />\n行去間餐廳12點9<br />\n去到排隊落單等完野食12點11<br />\n<br />\n行返office就已經1點<br />\n<br />\n個飯食到一半撳緊電話唔覺意望到已經13:17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔撚憤氣扮唔知<br />\n<br />\n繼續撳電話上連登<br />\n<br />\n仲猶豫緊呢一個鐘究竟我做咗啲咩會過得咁快<br />\n<br />\n就開咗個post喺度鳩up<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母upup下就13:27"},{"pid":"ef8c1149213aebf94450df85853e0f9c74d76ea2","tid":2128600,"uid":87337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:28:41.000Z","msg":"執埋啲外賣垃圾又返埋位做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32e37d15c20d17310f6e6e061918fcc231d8c00","tid":2128600,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"叫外賣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5142e3c0b78f98a215ef7f25e72ebd31158f58b","tid":2128600,"uid":74848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"放開兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cf1b6aef4b1b40930e4ccb92640d3cc459f897","tid":2128600,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32e37d15c20d17310f6e6e061918fcc231d8c00","tid":2128600,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"叫外賣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:34:57.000Z","msg